    dc:description "Fig. 4. — A–D. Anopogammarus birsteini Derzhavin, 1945. ♀, 9.0 mm, X44039/Cr-1645-FEFU: A. Habitus from left side. B. Urosome. C. Head. D. Metasomal and urosomal segments with telson. — E–G. Zenkevitchia sandroruffoi sp. nov. Paratype, ♀, 6.3 mm, X44045/Cr-1651-FEFU. E. Lateralia. F. Head. G. Urosome. — H–K. Adaugammarus pilosus sp. nov. Holotype, ♀, 13.5 mm, X44046/Cr- 1652-FEFU. H. Lateralia. I. Head. J. Urosome. K. Lateralia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3805945/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3805949>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Anopogammarus birsteini Derzhavin, 1945. ♀, 9.0 mm, X44039/Cr-1645-FEFU. A. Antenna 1. B. Antenna 2. C–D. Palmar margins of gnathopods 1 and 2 propodi. E. Maxilla 1. F. Outer plate of maxilla 1. G. Palp of right maxilla 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3805949/files/figure.png" ;
