<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3805953>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Anopogammarus birsteini Derzhavin, 1945. ♀, 9.0 mm, X44039/Cr-1645-FEFU. A. Pleopod 2. B. Coupling setae of pleopod 2. C. Uropod 1. D. Uropod 2. E–F. Uropod 3. G. Telson." ;
